== 7. Nxc4 ==
White recaptures the c4 pawn.

Black can now choose to either enter the Carlsbad variation with [[/7...Qc7|'''7...Qc7''']] or to transfer the knight to b6 with [[/7...Nb6|'''7...Nb6''']].

